query:
SELECT se.id, se.subjectId, se.professorId, s.name as subject_name
FROM student_enrollments se 
JOIN subjects s ON se.subjectId = s.id
WHERE se.studentId = 1
ORDER BY se.id DESC
LIMIT 5;
